{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/SteamGameplayOverviewGIF.gif?t=1683750419\" /><br><strong>BountyHeart</strong> is a twist on <strong>roguelikes</strong> that combines <strong>Match 3</strong> with<strong> Tactical Turn Based Combat</strong>! Each run, you will recruit a party and upgrade them with powerful items in an attempt to capture the Legendary Bounty!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OVERVIEW</h2>Move your characters in order to make <strong>matches </strong>of 3 or more orbs!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/SteamCoreMechanicGif.gif?t=1683750419\" /><br><br>By matching Attack Orbs <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/smallattack.png?t=1683750419\" /> or Charisma Orbs <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/smallcharisma.png?t=1683750419\" />, you can either<strong> KILL </strong>or <strong>RECRUIT</strong> the enemies you encounter on your journey. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/KillOrRecruitSmall.png?t=1683750419\" /><br><br>Killing the enemy allows you to claim their <strong>BOUNTY</strong>, granting you gold and powerful items to upgrade your party. <br><br>Recruiting the enemy allows you to add new members to your <strong>PARTY</strong> and make the best crew possible!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ITEMS</h2>Along your journey, you will discover items that buff your characters in unique ways. Combine them with your characters to create powerful builds for your party. Each run is different, so there will be new combinations to discover every time!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/SteamPageFatures.png?t=1683750419\" /><br>- <strong>Over 20 characters</strong> with unique abilities and stats to encounter and recruit!<br><br>- <strong>50 different items</strong> to mix and match to upgrade your party!<br><br>- <strong>Replayable Roguelite Fun</strong>. Each run is different! Adapt and strategize based on the choices you\u2019re given.<br><br>- Varying Ascension levels to unlock to add even more replayability!<br><br>- A beautiful score composed by <strong>Alex Meade</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997120/extras/bountyheartcharorbsgif.gif?t=1683750419\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Prison Escaped?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/02edd9cea83d86570e8cdb1b1a4a50c65c9cb705.jpg"},{"name":"Veteran Crewmate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/d32ad85ad166d2422a655ffe3ad594a973de67a8.jpg"},{"name":"Fabled Crewmate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/2225745ae62397dd6dfa9109ffb9d776197bdca2.jpg"},{"name":"Mythical Crewmate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/90ff7ddd9457ed4d0a685aa20b5505649c402c42.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Bounty Secured?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/ef33458dbdb41832b8eaa08421a8bf60e0e9c828.jpg"},{"name":"Adept Bounty Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/73e4daf6d02832f73888b87b991bbffe5c9fce11.jpg"},{"name":"Unreal Bounty Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/c89be9af8e8f3c72b12d1ae3d34b107e30c7f6a3.jpg"},{"name":"Unspeakable Bounty Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1997120/afe7b09e2a9970c9207a3e25db5e92180239ea9d.jpg"},{"name":"Common Item